data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven is a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, offering a lifestyle that truly embraces the essence of Southern living. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere, complemented by a cozy fireplace that creates the perfect setting for relaxation. You'll be delighted to discover a generously sized fenced-in yard. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or simply enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this backyard oasis is a true retreat. Convenience is key, and this home delivers. Situated in Raeford, you'll find yourself just a stone's throw away from a plenty of restaurants, shopping, and more! From quaint local eateries to bustling retail centers, everything you need is within reach, making daily life a breeze. Pets allowed with a non-refundable pet fee and monthly pet rent. Nest does not accept applications through third party listing sites. Enrollment in Resident Benefit Package mandatory at cost of $30/month.
